g the world bank and the federal communications commission and as a board member and advisor to high technology financial and startup companies in the area of auctions business strategy antitrust and regulation he also serves as an advisory board member for sustainable conservation and the nepal youth opportunity fund curriculum vitae publications competitive implications of the proposed acquisition of t mobile by at&t mobility march 2011 policy brief using spectrum auctions to enhance competition in wireless services february 2011 discussion paper stanford university economics department stanford center for international development public policy program site map economic summit
